  "prompt": "What is the best digital marketing course in Kolkata?",
  "response": "Choosing the best digital marketing course in Kolkata can depend on various factors such as the curriculum, faculty, duration, fees, and placement opportunities. Some highly acclaimed digital marketing courses in Kolkata include:\n\n1. **Indian Institute of Social Welfare and Business Management (IISWBM):**\n   - Offers an Advanced Diploma in Digital Marketing.\n   - Known for its comprehensive curriculum and experienced faculty.\n\n2. **Kolkata Digital Marketing Institute (KDMI):**\n   - Provides a variety of digital marketing courses with practical training.\n   - Focuses on hands-on experience and live projects.\n\n3. **EduPristine:**\n   - Has a digital marketing certification program.\n   - Known for industry-aligned curriculum and expert trainers.\n\n4. **Seven Boats Academy:**\n   - Offers online and offline digital marketing courses.\n   - Covers topics like SEO, SEM, SMM, content marketing, and more.\n\n5. **NIHT Digital Marketing:**\n   - Provides Professional Diploma in Digital Marketing.\n   - Known for its detailed modules and placement assistance.\n\n6. **IMPACT Institute:**\n   - Offers intensive digital marketing training programs.\n   - Renowned for practical approach and client project exposure.\n\nIt's advisable to visit the websites of these institutes, check their course details, and reviews, and if possible, connect with alumni for a better understanding before making a decision.",
